data.description: This is the ONE!  Desirable Canyon Creek Ranch Home Located in a Cul De Saq & Tucked in the Trees, This Picture Perfect Family Home has Everything You Desire, Entertain Effortlessly in Your Own Backyard Oasis Featuring Outdoor Kitchen & Living Center Complete with WBFP & Bar Overlooking the Sparkling Diving Pool & Waterfall, Lush Landscaping, Abundant Seclusion & Privacy,  Step Inside to Find a Functional Traditional Floorplan with Over 3700 Square Feet, 4 Beds, 3.5 Baths,  Extensive Trimwork & Moldings Throughout,  Cozy Living Room with a Wall of Windows & Handsome Stone FP,   Kitchen Features Custom Cabinets, Granite & Work Island, Gorgeous Hardwood Floors, Study with French Doors & Extra Storage, Formal Dining, Oversized Master Suite, Double Staircases Lead Upstairs to Bedrooms with Built Ins & Jack N Jill Bath, Spacious Gameroom with Endless Possibilities, 29x20 Shop with Electricity, Storm Shelter, Water Well, BROCK ISD!  This Well Cared for Home is All You’ve Been Looking For!
